    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems so much easier to go the natural route. if i take a lot of garlic extract and drink lots of green juices, it's basically the same thing as being on a thinner, right? like, if i just gradually taper off the warfarin while i ramp up the supplements, wouldn't that be a safe way to switch over? i just want to get away from the chemicals.",
