      "content": "Tapering off warfarin while ramping up supplements is an incredibly risky maneuver that could lead to a massive blood clot or severe bleeding. You cannot safely \"switch\" from a prescription anticoagulant to dietary supplements without constant, professional monitoring. If you want to reduce your reliance on chemicals, you must discuss a *controlled* dosage adjustment with your prescribing physician, not attempt a self-managed detox.",
